<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-07-26T11:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-07-26T11:29:00-05:00" n="324" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d324">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.51/252</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-26T11:00:00-05:29">
                                        <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1917, 11 a.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>My telegram of July 24, noon. Congress accepted veto and House passed
                                new measure satisfactory to President except that tax on iron and
                                copper too high. He hopes to get Senate pass same bill before
                                adjournment that is imminent, and will suspend part of iron and
                                copper tax expecting reduction by Congress next winter.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>